    "en": {
      "title": "Don't let accusations arise about buying rice",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Agriculture Minister Mahinda Amaraweera ordered the Paddy Marketing Board not to allow any accusations to be made by the farmers regarding the purchase of paddy.",
        "The minister said to take steps to buy paddy at the same price and not to harass the farmers for any reason.",
        "The Ministry of Agriculture says that the Paddy Marketing Board has taken all measures to start the procurement of paddy in the Yala season from today (17).",
        "The Minister of Agriculture advised the Paddy Marketing Board to end all the defects that may arise in the purchase of paddy today and to arrange for the purchase without any defects by all regional offices of the Paddy Marketing Board from tomorrow (18).",
        "The Paddy Marketing Board is also issuing a circular to all regional managers to prepare all the equipment related to the purchase of paddy, such as moisture measuring devices, weighing devices etc.",
        "There are 07 regional offices under the Paddy Marketing Board and there are 310 paddy warehouses under it."
      ],
